SNPs <- read.table("23andMe_complete.txt", header = TRUE, sep = "\t")

Example 1

ggplot(SNPs,aes(SNPs$chromosome,color=SNPs$chromosome))+geom_bar()

Example 2

ggplot(SNPs,aes(reorder(chromosome,chromosome,
                        function(x)-length(x)),color=SNPs$chromosome))+geom_bar()

Example 3

ggplot(SNPs,aes(SNPs$chromosome,fill=SNPs$genotype))+geom_bar()

Example 4

ggplot(SNPs,aes(SNPs$chromosome,fill=SNPs$genotype))+geom_bar(position="fill")
